    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Sibbaeus Eron<lb break="no" n="2"/>is <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> tubicen ex <lb n="3"/>cohorte I <lb n="4"/>Ituraeorum <lb n="5"/>miles <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXIV <lb n="6"/>stipendiorum <lb n="7"/>VIII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Grabstele mit Aediculanische, darin halbfigurige Darstellung eines Mannes in Tunica und Mantel, in der Rechten die zerlegte tuba.</p>
            </div>
